Package: ndpresponder
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Lucas Kafarski
Description: IPv6 Neighbor Discovery Protocol Responder
 A high-performance C implementation of an IPv6 NDP responder that handles
 neighbor solicitations for configured subnets and Docker containers.
 .
 Features include support for excluded subnets, Docker container monitoring,
 gratuitous neighbor advertisements, and configurable response policies.
 The implementation is optimized for low memory usage and high performance.
Depends: libnet1
Recommends: iputils-ping
Homepage: https://github.com/a2hop/ndpresponder-c
